name: OM BSA Enterprises
overview:
We, an ISO-9001:2000 certified company, have been in this business since 1987 because of which, we have been able to gather required proficiency in the industry to cater to the diverse requirements of industries such as engineering, medical and others. Each of our precision component, CNC components and CNC precision turned components are in confirmation with the industry quality standard.

We have a manufacturing unit well equipped with high-end machines because of which we always remain in the best position to undertake assignment in bulk. Moreover, we also assure to complete the same within promised time frame.
